### Prueba Directa del Servidor MCP

### 1. Probar el servidor MCP directamente (sin nuestra API)
POST http://localhost:8970
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "test-1",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}

### 2. Probar con método diferente
POST http://localhost:8970
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "test-2",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}

### 3. Probar con método initialize
POST http://localhost:8970
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "test-3",
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "TestClient",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

### 4. Probar con método vacío (para ver el error)
POST http://localhost:8970
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "test-4",
  "method": "",
  "params": {}
